subtitleNullable: Train data for Enefit competition with secondary features in parquet
descriptionNullable:
This is the pre-processed dataset for the Enefit competition. This dataset inputs the train data from the competition, builds secondary features and outputs it here. We will develop this dataset as we move along in the competition. This data is used as input to the model development and inferencing kernel.
Preprocessing kernel link- https://www.kaggle.com/code/ravi20076/enefit-traindataprep
